Daymi m'ara n-aseɣ ɣuṛ-wen a d-sbeggneɣ akk ayen ixeddem ! Iheddeṛ fell-aneɣ yir imeslayen akk-d lekdub, ula d atmaten yugi ad yesṭerḥeb yis-sen, wid yebɣan ad sṭerḥben yis-sen, yețțaggi-yasen yerna yessufuɣ-iten si lḥebs.
Ass n Lɛid n wass wis xemsin, inelmaden llan nnejmaɛen akk deg wayen yedṛan. Uzza d wayen yellan deg-sen, ț-țamdint n Sinay neɣ ț-țemdint n Antyuc, qqimen yid-sen i leǧnas nniḍen.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass i deg ara nsel i ṣṣut n lbuq n wass amezwaru, imiren kra wussan-nni ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail, a d-sbeggnen ṭṭaɛa-nsen ɣer Sidi Ṛebbi seg waṭas n uqehheṛ ; ayen i d-iteddun anagar deg ussan-nni ur nezmir a t-nekkes ara.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen ur sɛin ara ddunit, wiyaḍ d imdanen i sen-ț-ikksen.
?ef wayen yeɛnan lɛid n iɛejmiyen d iqelwacen akk-d sebɛa n yergazen nniḍen i d-yusan si tmurt n Nefṭali, azal n meyya uṛebɛa uṛebɛin wagguren.
sbubben-as amekkas n tebzert, isem-is Malṭa, zeddiget n tẓurin ; ma yella wamek ara yili wučči ț-țaḥeṛṛit .
M'ara d-yas Sidna Ɛisa ixṣimen n Qayṣer, i glaq ad iṛuḥ ɣer wexxam n Qayṣer ; yefka lameṛ a d-sseɣlin deg wexxam n ccṛeɛ iwakken ad ccetkin fell-as.
S wakka ihi, m'ara d-inṭeq, init-ed kan i lǧețța n Sidna Ɛisa ; imiren kan, lehna-nsen ad uɣalen d imeṛkantiyen.
M'ara tedduklem ɣer imensi n usmekti, mkul amkan n lḥekma, a kkun-id-yefk ula d kunwi s lḥut mbla lɛib.
Tazzla deg wannar d ayen yelhan meɛna tenfeɛ i lǧețța kan, ma ṭṭaɛa n Sidi Ṛebbi tenfeɛ i kullec axaṭer deg-s i tella tudert n tura akk-d ț-țin i d-iteddun i ɣ-iwɛed Sidi Ṛebbi.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg wedrar n Siyun alamma tella yiwet n tama tayeffust n Sidi Ṛebbi di ṭṭlam, a wen-d-yefk daɣen lerwaǧ, d itri-nni i gzemren aț-țawḍem ɣer teddawiḍ.
Llan daɣen kra n wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi si lebɛid. Llan deg idurar, d wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, iwumi i d-yessawel, i nețța isem-is Isḥaq, Yeɛqub, mmi-s n weḥḥed-sen akk-d tmeṭṭut-nsen.
Heggit iman-nwen ula d kunwi imi di lebḥeṛ, abeɛda wid i ten-yufan anagar ma yella ɣef ddemma n yisem n Sidna Ɛisa, ur nelli ara seg wat Isṛail ;
Ajelkkiḍ-is yezzuɣeṛ-ed aman i gelhan. Eɛni ilaq ad yili win ara iceɛlen taftilt iwakken a ț-yerr aman ?
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
Akken daɣen ula d nutni ṭeggiṛen leḥwayeǧ nsen akk-d wid yețțaɣen znuzun leḥwayeǧ di leqdic,
Lɛid i deg xeddmen aɣṛum mbla iɣes n temtunt ( iɣes n temtunt ) yellan d Ɛisa Lmasiḥ.
Aṭas n yemdanen i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen ur sɛin ara ddunit, wiyaḍ d imdanen i sen-ț-ikksen.
Lɛid i deg xedmen aɣṛum mbla iɣes n temtunt ițțusemman « Tafaska n izimer n leslak » tqeṛb-ed iwakken a s-fken lǧețța n Sidna Ɛisa.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen ur sɛin ara ddunit, wiyaḍ d imdanen i sen-ț-ikksen.
Ass n westeɛfu nniḍen, qṛib tamdint n Antyuc. Ass n lɛid n Tfaska n weɣṛum mbla tamtunt ( iɣes ), i deg zellun imensi n Tfaska n izimer n leslak, i luḍu. Tameddit n wass n Tfaska n izimer ț-țemdint n leslak n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Mkul amdan, ilaq ad iqadeṛ imdebbṛen i gḥekkmen tamurt i deg yețɛici, yusa-d ɣer dagi anagar deg umkan yexlan.
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tewwurt, acḥal yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer tudert yerna drus i gețɛeddayen syenna.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen wergaz n usqamu n waman, llan gar-asen, ulli ur nesɛi lɛib, zzux, d iɛdawen n mkul ṣṣenf.
Ma yella daɣen ț-țiṭ-is neɣ tilemẓit, qleɛ-iț tmes, tḍegṛeḍ-t akkin fell-ak. ?ader iman-nwen aț-țilim d sebba n uɣelluy i gma-s.
D wagi i d lweqt i deg ara yedṛun annect-agi ? Akken kan i gessen tazeggaɣit yellan deg igenwan, yețwarfed ɣer igenni, asm'ara ɛeddin lweqt i deg ara d-iteddun alamma ț-țamecṭuḥt ;
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-ines a s-tṛuḥ. Akka ara tedṛu d umeṛkanti , ad iṛuḥ a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es wayen akk yesɛa.
Ilaq-aɣ ihi a d-nextiṛ yiwen seg wid yellan yid-es, mačči d amdan i gesɛan azal meɛna d lameṛ n ddunit ; wid yellan daɣen i gxeddmen annect-agi, d ayen ur nețdum ara ula d nutni.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
ț-țamhennit, treggin-aɣ-d llebsa tamellalt, ṭṭfen-d deg idmaren-nsen akken yella di lɛadda-nsen.
Ma d wid yettabaɛen cci n ddunit ɣellin deg ujeṛṛeb akk-d tfextin n yir ccehwat n tnefsit-nsen, i gețțawin imdanen ɣer txeṣṣart akk-d nnger.
